Kuki imvubu zitagira umusatsi?

Umunsi umwe, Urukwavu rwagendagendaga hafi y'inzuzi.

Imvubu nayo, Yajyaga ijya gutembera no kurya ibyatsi byiza.

Kubw"impanuka imvubu yakandagiye ikirenge cy'urukwavu ariko imvubu itabibonye.

Urukwavu rurataka ruti, "Wa mvubu we! Ntushobora kubona ko ukandagiye ikirenge cyanjye?"

Imvubu yasabye imbabazi Urukwavu, "Ndababaye cyane. Sinari nakubonye. Nyamuneka umbabarire!"

Ariko Urukwavu ntirwabyumva maze rusubiza imvubu n'uburakari ruti: "Ibyo wabikoze ubigambiriye! Umunsi umwe, uzambona! giye ku kwishyura!"

Urukwavu rwagiye gushaka umuriro, rubwira umuriro ruti: "Genda, utwike imvubu niva mu mazi ije kurya ibyatsi.
Yankandagiye!"

Umuriro usubiza urukwavu ruti: "Ntakibazo, Urukwavu, nshuti yanjye. Ndakora ibyo usabye."

Bidatinze, Imvubu yagiye kurira ibyatsi kure yuruzi, Umuriro ugurumana uti:"Whoosh!" Umuriro watangiye gutwika umusatsi w'imvubu.

Imvubu yatangiye kurira, yirukira mu mazi. Umusatsi wose watwitswe n'umuriro.

Imvubu yakomeje kurira, iti  "Umusatsi wanjye watwitswe n'umuriro! Umusatsi wanjye wose urashize! 
Umusatsi wanjye mwiza!"

Urukwavu rwishimiye ko umusatsi w'Imvubu wahiye.

Kugeza n'uyu munsi, kubera gutinya umuriro, imvubu ntabwo igera kure y'amazi.
